name: TheFloorIsLavaRevival
title: The Floor Is Lava Revival
author: Weston Kelliher, Xorimuth, Noskcaj19
description:
Extreme radiation causes you to take damage unless you're on manmade tiles. A fun challenge for territory expansion.
Original mod by westoncraft, updated to 1.0 by Xorimuth, tweaks by Noskcaj19.
